  "title": "Sales Admin Coordinator (Luxury Retail) | CBD | Basic + Meal Allowance + Commission + Bonus",
  "description": "<p>📍 <strong>Location:</strong> Central Business District (CBD)<br>\n🕘 <strong>Working Hours:</strong> Retail hours (10am – 9pm), 5 days/week, including weekends and public holidays (off days on rotation)</p>\n<p>💰 <strong>Salary:</strong><br>\n• Basic: $1,800/month<br>\n• Fixed Allowance: $200 (Meal Allowance)<br>\n• OT Pay (after 44 hours)<br>\n• Commission<br>\n• AWS + Variable Bonus (non-contractual)</p>\n<p>✨ <strong>Benefits:</strong><br>\n• 14 Days Annual Leave<br>\n• Group Hospitalization Insurance<br>\n• Outpatient and Dental Coverage</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>👗 <strong>Job Scope:</strong><br>\n• Sales &amp; Purchase administrative support (data entry, order processing)<br>\n• Inventory management and reconciliation<br>\n• Cash handling (cards, petty cash, etc.)<br>\n• Coordination with HQ and other departments<br>\n• Ensure smooth administrative operations in assigned boutique<br>\n• Dissemination of memos and communications to boutique staff<br>\n• Filing and documentation<br>\n• Any other ad-hoc duties assigned by HQ</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>🎯 <strong>Requirements:</strong><br>\n• GCE ‘N’ / ‘O’ Level or above<br>\n• Proficient in Microsoft Excel and Word<br>\n• Able to multi-task and work independently<br>\n• Must be able to work retail hours, weekends &amp; PHs<br>\n• Bilingual in English and Mandarin (to liaise with Mandarin-speaking customers)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>EA Personnel Name: Jabez Wong<br>\nEA Personnel No: R1762582<br>\nEA License No: 23C1703</p>",
